 class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistContainer" id="RegularArticle-WatchlistDropdown" data-analytics-id="RegularArticle-WatchlistDropdown"><button class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-addWatchListFromTag"></span></button></span></li><li class="QuoteItem-item" aria-label="Quote for null"> <a href="https://www.cnbc.com/quotes/AXP" class="QuoteItem-link"><span class="QuoteItem-symbol">AXP</span></a> <span class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistContainer" id="RegularArticle-WatchlistDropdown" data-analytics-id="RegularArticle-WatchlistDropdown"><button class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-addWatchListFromTag"></span></button></span></li><li class="QuoteItem-item" aria-label="Quote for null"><a href="https://www.cnbc.com/quotes/NVDA" class="QuoteItem-link"><span class="QuoteItem-symbol">英伟达</span></a><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistContainer" id="RegularArticle-WatchlistDropdown" data-analytics-id="RegularArticle-WatchlistDropdown"><button class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-addWatchListFromTag"></span></button></span></li><li class="QuoteItem-item" aria-label="Quote for null"><a href="https://www.cnbc.com/quotes/RH" class="QuoteItem-link"><span class="QuoteItem-symbol">相对湿度</span></a><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistContainer" id="RegularArticle-WatchlistDropdown" data-analytics-id="RegularArticle-WatchlistDropdown"><button class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-addWatchListFromTag"></span></button></span></li><li class="QuoteItem-item" aria-label="Quote for null"> <a href="https://www.cnbc.com/quotes/F" class="QuoteItem-link"><span class="QuoteItem-symbol">F</span></a> <span class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistContainer" id="RegularArticle-WatchlistDropdown" data-analytics-id="RegularArticle-WatchlistDropdown"><button class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-addWatchListFromTag"></span></button></span></li></ul></div><div class="RelatedQuotes-cfaButtonContainer"> <button id="ArticlePageTickerCreateAccountButton" class="CreateFreeAccountButton-buttonContainer"><span class="CreateFreeAccountButton-buttonText"><span>关注您最喜爱的股票</span><span class="CreateFreeAccountButton-buttonTextBold">创建免费账户</span></span></button></div></div><div class="InlineImage-imageEmbed" id="ArticleBody-InlineImage-107221091" data-test="InlineImage"><div class="InlineImage-wrapper"><div class="InlineImage-imagePlaceholder" style="padding-bottom:55.55555555555556%"><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div></div><div><div class="InlineImage-imageEmbedCaption"> 2022 年纽约国际车展上的福特 F-150 Lightning Platinum 电动卡车。</div><div class="InlineImage-imageEmbedCredit">迈克尔·内格尔 |彭博 |盖蒂图片社</div></div></div></div><div class="group"><p><em>查看周五中午做出最大动作的公司。</em></p><p> <span class="QuoteInBody-quoteNameContainer" data-test="QuoteInBody" id="RegularArticle-QuoteInBody-1"><a href="https://www.cnbc.com/quotes/F/">福特</a><span class="QuoteInBody-inlineButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistContainer" id="-WatchlistDropdown" data-analytics-id="-WatchlistDropdown"><button class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-addWatchListFromTag"></span></button></span></span></span> — 周四晚些时候<a href="https://www.cnbc.com/2023/05/25/tesla-elon-musk-ford-jim-farley-ev-twitter-spaces-talk.html">，福特和特斯拉宣布建立合作伙伴关系</a>后，股价暴涨约 7%，这将使福特车主能够在美国和加拿大使用超过 12,000 个特斯拉增压器。 <span class="QuoteInBody-quoteNameContainer" data-test="QuoteInBody" id="RegularArticle-QuoteInBody-3"><a href="https://www.cnbc.com/quotes/TSLA/">特斯拉</a><span class="QuoteInBody-inlineButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistContainer" id="-WatchlistDropdown" data-analytics-id="-WatchlistDropdown"><button class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-addWatchListFromTag"></span></button></span></span></span>的股票上涨了 5%。 </p><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div><div class="ExclusiveContentBucket-exclusiveContentBucket"><span class="ExclusiveContentBucket-smallSpan"></span><span class="ExclusiveContentBucket-border"></span><h2 class="ExclusiveContentBucket-exclusiveContentHeading">相关投资新闻</h2><div class="ExclusiveContentBucket-contentContainer"><div class="BucketItem-bucketItem" id="Regular Article-ExclusiveContentBucket-1-0"><div class="BucketItem-bucketImageContainer"><img class="BucketItem-bucketImage BucketItem-investingClubItem" src="https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/107213551-1679578993460-107213551-16795140722023-03-22t193227z_1723134562_rc26zz9gts9n_rtrmadp_0_usa-stocks.jpg?v=1685107571" alt="长周末前周五我们在股市上关注的 10 件事" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="BucketItem-proPillContainer"></div><div class="BucketItem-investingClubPillContainer"> <a href="https://www.cnbc.com/investingclub/" class="InvestingClubPill-investingClubPillLink" data-type="investing-club-button"><img class="BucketItem-investingClubPill InvestingClubPill-investingClubPill" src="https://static-redesign.cnbcfm.com/dist/b0b683565c27c5457864.svg" alt="CNBC 投资俱乐部" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></a> </div></div><div class="BucketItem-textContainer BucketItem-icTextContainer"><div class="BucketItem-title"> <a href="https://www.cnbc.com/2023/05/26/the-clubs-10-things-to-watch-in-the-stock-market-friday.html">长周末前周五我们在股市上关注的 10 件事</a></div><div class="BucketItem-bylineContainer"><div><div class="BucketItemByline-author"><a href="https://www.cnbc.com/matthew-j-belvedere/">马修·J·丽城</a></div></div><div class="BucketItem-publishTime">4小时前</div></div></div></div></div></div><p><span class="QuoteInBody-quoteNameContainer" data-test="QuoteInBody" id="RegularArticle-QuoteInBody-4"><a href="https://www.cnbc.com/quotes/MRVL/">美满科技</a><span class="QuoteInBody-inlineButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistContainer" id="-WatchlistDropdown" data-analytics-id="-WatchlistDropdown"><button class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-addWatchListFromTag"></span></button></span></span></span> — 在公司收益超过分析师预期后，半导体股票飙升 28%。 Marvell Technology 还预计收入增长将在本财年下半年加速，首席执行官马特墨菲称人工智能是“关键增长动力”。</p><p> <span class="QuoteInBody-quoteNameContainer" data-test="QuoteInBody" id="RegularArticle-QuoteInBody-5"><a href="https://www.cnbc.com/quotes/ULTA/">乌尔塔美容</a><span class="QuoteInBody-inlineButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistContainer" id="-WatchlistDropdown" data-analytics-id="-WatchlistDropdown"><button class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-addWatchListFromTag"></span></button></span></span></span> — 在公司公布第一季度财报后，这家美容零售商的股价下跌超过 12%。尽管报告盈利和收入好于预期，但由于公司全年营业利润率前景下调，股价下跌。</p><p> <span class="QuoteInBody-quoteNameContainer" data-test="QuoteInBody" id="RegularArticle-QuoteInBody-6"><a href="https://www.cnbc.com/quotes/PARA/">派拉蒙</a><span class="QuoteInBody-inlineButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistContainer" id="-WatchlistDropdown" data-analytics-id="-WatchlistDropdown"><button class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-addWatchListFromTag"></span></button></span></span></span> — 在派拉蒙的多数投票股东 National Amusements <a href="https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20230525005840/en/National-Amusements-Announces-Strategic-Investment-from-BDT-MSD-Partners" target="_blank">宣布 BDT Capital Partners 进行 1.25 亿美元</a>的优先股权投资后，这家媒体公司的股价上涨了 5% 以上。鉴于该消息，Loop Capital 将派拉蒙评级从卖出上调至持有。这家华尔街公司表示，牛市案例是财务压力将迫使派拉蒙寻找买家，股东将实现私人市场价值。</p><p> <span class="QuoteInBody-quoteNameContainer" data-test="QuoteInBody" id="RegularArticle-QuoteInBody-8"><a href="https://www.cnbc.com/quotes/GPS/">差距</a><span class="QuoteInBody-inlineButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistContainer" id="-WatchlistDropdown" data-analytics-id="-WatchlistDropdown"><button class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-addWatchListFromTag"></span></button></span></span></span> — 这家服装零售商的股价在周四公布<a href="https://www.cnbc.com/2023/05/25/gap-gps-q1-earnings-report-2023.html">最近一个季度的</a>净亏损和销售额下降后仍上涨了 11%。投资者为 Gap 利润率的大幅提高而欢呼，这归因于促销活动的减少和空运费用的降低。</p><p> <span class="QuoteInBody-quoteNameContainer" data-test="QuoteInBody" id="RegularArticle-QuoteInBody-10"><a href="https://www.cnbc.com/quotes/WDAY/">工作日</a><span class="QuoteInBody-inlineButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistContainer" id="-WatchlistDropdown" data-analytics-id="-WatchlistDropdown"><button class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-addWatchListFromTag"></span></button></span></span></span> — 在第一季度收益和收入超出分析师预期后，该股上涨超过 11.1%。 Workday 还提高了全年订阅收入指引的下限，并任命了新的首席财务官 Zane Rowe。</p><div style="height:100%" class="lazyload-placeholder"></div><p> <span class="QuoteInBody-quoteNameContainer" data-test="QuoteInBody" id="RegularArticle-QuoteInBody-11"><a href="https://www.cnbc.com/quotes/RH/">相对湿度</a><span class="QuoteInBody-inlineButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistContainer" id="-WatchlistDropdown" data-analytics-id="-WatchlistDropdown"><button class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-addWatchListFromTag"></span></button></span></span></span> — 在该零售商第二季度业绩指引未达到分析师预期后，股价下跌约 3.7%。该公司还警告说，降价幅度会增加。然而，RH 在周四收盘后公布业绩时超出了 Refinitiv 对第一季度调整后每股收益和收入的预期。</p><p> <span class="QuoteInBody-quoteNameContainer" data-test="QuoteInBody" id="RegularArticle-QuoteInBody-12"><a href="https://www.cnbc.com/quotes/DECK/">德克斯户外</a><span class="QuoteInBody-inlineButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistContainer" id="-WatchlistDropdown" data-analytics-id="-WatchlistDropdown"><button class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-addWatchListFromTag"></span></button></span></span></span> — Deckers Outdoor 股价上涨 2.3%，此前这家支持 Ugg 和 HOKA 鞋履的鞋类公司公布了超出分析师预期的第四财季业绩。然而，它给出的全年收益和收入指引低于预期。</p><p> <span class="QuoteInBody-quoteNameContainer" data-test="QuoteInBody" id="RegularArticle-QuoteInBody-13"><a href="https://www.cnbc.com/quotes/AXP/">美国运通</a><span class="QuoteInBody-inlineButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistContainer" id="-WatchlistDropdown" data-analytics-id="-WatchlistDropdown"><button class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-addWatchListFromTag"></span></button></span></span></span> — 股价在午盘交易中上涨超过 3%。周五，摩根士丹利表示，最近的抛售“过度”，该股处于多年来最低水平，对投资者来说是一个<a href="https://www.cnbc.com/2023/05/26/american-express-is-a-top-pick-that-can-rally-more-than-20percent-morgan-stanley-says.html">很好的切入点</a>。</p><p> <span class="QuoteInBody-quoteNameContainer" data-test="QuoteInBody" id="RegularArticle-QuoteInBody-15"><a href="https://www.cnbc.com/quotes/NVDA/">英伟达</a><span class="QuoteInBody-inlineButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistContainer" id="-WatchlistDropdown" data-analytics-id="-WatchlistDropdown"><button class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-addWatchListFromTag"></span></button></span></span></span> — 半导体股票上涨 1.7%，此前一天在 AI 宠儿的井喷收益报告的支持下<a href="https://www.cnbc.com/2023/05/25/nvidia-on-track-for-record-high-driven-by-ai-chip-demand.html">飙升 24%</a> 。周五的走高使 Nvidia 的市值接近 1 万亿美元。</p><p> <span class="QuoteInBody-quoteNameContainer" data-test="QuoteInBody" id="RegularArticle-QuoteInBody-17"><a href="https://www.cnbc.com/quotes/MPWR/">单片电源系统</a><span class="QuoteInBody-inlineButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistContainer" id="-WatchlistDropdown" data-analytics-id="-WatchlistDropdown"><button class="AddToWatchlistButton-watchlistButton"><span class="AddToWatchlistButton-addWatchListFromTag"></span></button></span></span></span> - 该股票是从 Nvidia 的收益报告和对 AI 的兴奋中获得提振的股票之一。 Monolithic Power Systems 上涨 6.7%，而 Arista Networks 上涨 8.1%。 Broadcom 上涨 7%，NXP Semiconductors 上涨 4.4%，Adobe 也上涨 4.4%。</p><p> <em>— CNBC 的 Hakyung Kim、Yun Li、Tanaya Macheel 和 Sarah Min 提供了报道。</em> </p></div><div id="ArticleBody-MobileAdhesion" class="MobileAdhesion-container" data-module="mps-slot"></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Fri, 26 May 2023 17:06:06 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> 107247306</guid><link/> https://www.cnbc.com/2023/05/26/stocks-making-the-biggest-moves-midday-ford-marvell-technology-paramount-gap-more.html<author><![CDATA[Michelle Fox]]></author><category>全国广播公司</category><category>文章</category><category>单片电源系统公司</category><category>马维尔科技公司</category><category>派拉蒙全球</category><category>差距公司</category><category>工作日公司</category><category>Ulta 美容公司</category><category>德克斯户外公司</category><category>美国运通公司</category><category>英伟达公司</category><category>相对湿度</category><category>特斯拉公司</category><category>福特汽车公司</category><category>市场内幕</category><category>市场</category><category>经济</category><category>商业</category><category>股市</category><category>突发新闻：市场</category><category>人工智能</category><category>金融</category><category>股票</category><category>美国市场</category><category>来源：标签名称：CNBC 美国来源</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Taylor Swift is this summer's most in-demand artist—Eras Tour tickets sell for an average of $920]]></title><description><![CDATA[Taylor Swift is this summer's most in-demand artist—Eras Tour tickets sell for an average of $920]]></description><pubDate> Fri, 26 May 2023 17:06:00 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> 107247217</guid><link/> https://www.cnbc.com/2023/05/26/taylor-swift-beyonc-metallica-summer-2023s-top-10-hottest-artist-.html<author><![CDATA[Nicolas Vega]]></author><category>做了</category><category>文章</category><category>周末</category><category>粉色的</category><category>乔治海峡</category><category>布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀</category><category>艾德·希兰</category><category>碧昂丝</category><category>泰勒斯威夫特</category><category>做了</category><category>做它 - 生活</category><category>成功 - 流行文化</category><category>来源：标签名称：CNBC 美国来源</category></item></channel></rss>